CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 2, 1961, pg. 2B reads: "Miller, Belmar Students Visit Flower Show- Wide-eyed visitors, captivated by the beauty of the Flower Show, included students [form] Belmar and Miller Street Schools...In the botto[m]n photo, Mrs. Frances Brown, teacher, shoulders the responsibility for the Miller school students. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Miller Street school students with teacher Frances Brown, standing in Phipps Conservatory
